    "body": "> I disagree, having the stackoverflow button \"hidden\" at the bottom of the menu doesn't make sense.\n\nYes ok.\n\nTBH I think I do not see the exact value of linking to stackoverflow since I would first go to github issues. I would have a hard time deciding if I need to post on stackoverflow OR github since I have both links = Should we split our issues between SO and github right away, how will the user decides?\n",
